==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cellar
<hw>Cel"lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>celer</ets>,
OF. <ets>celier</ets>, F. <ets>celier</ets>, fr. L. <ets>cellarium</ets>
a receptacle for food, pantry, fr. <ets>cella</ets> storeroom. See
<er>Cell</er>.]</ety> <def>A room or rooms under a building, and usually
below the surface of the ground, where provisions and other stores are
kept.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cellarage</ent>⟦br⟧
